parameters.name: TIME_TAG
parameters.description:
The Mission Elapsed Time (MET) in seconds               
        when the LVPS X,Y,Z axis samples were collected.

parameters.name: ACTUAL_RANGE
parameters.description: Actual Range used by MAG. =0 1530 nT, =1 51300 nT

parameters.name: STATUS_CNT_SENSOR_X
parameters.description:
The LVPS X-axis sample. X axis field value in signed    
      integer counts. If DN value is greater than 8192 then this value is     
      DN - 16384. DN is the telemetry value stored in the downloaded packet.

parameters.name: STATUS_CNT_SENSOR_Y
parameters.description:
The LVPS Y-axis sample. Y axis field value in signed    
      integer counts. If DN value is greater than 8192 then this value is     
      DN - 16384. DN is the telemetry value stored in the downloaded packet.

parameters.name: STATUS_CNT_SENSOR_Z
parameters.description:
The LVPS Z-axis sample. Z axis field value in signed    
      integer counts. If DN value is greater than 8192 then this value is     
      DN - 16384. DN is the telemetry value stored in the downloaded packet.

parameters.name: MAG_DC_DC_CURR
parameters.description:
The derived MAG DC/DC current; used the following       
                      formula:                                                
                      If the DN value is less than 128,                       
                        MAG_DC_DC_CURR = DN/64                                
                      else                                                    
                        MAG_DC_DC_CURR = (DN-256)/64.                         
                      Where DN is the telemetry value.

parameters.name: MAG_ELEC_TEMP
parameters.description:
The derived MAG electronics temperature; used the       
      following formula:                                                      
      MAG_ELEC_TEMP = (155*DN/127) - 55                                       
      Where DN is the telemetry value.

parameters.name: MAG_PROBE_TEMP
parameters.description: The raw telemetry counts for the MAG probe temperature.

parameters.name: LVPS_PLUS5V
parameters.description:
The raw integer counts for LVPS +5 voltage counter.     
      The values for this column are set to an N/A value of 999 when          
      FSW_VERSION is less than 9; the measurement did not exist in prior      
      flight software versions.
